error: #[immune] accepts either `witness = ...` or `requires = ...`, not both. For compound evidence across code-tier and substrate-tier (e.g., hybrid antigens per ADR-028), stack two `#[immune]` attributes on the same item — one with `witness = ...`, one with `requires = ...`. Audit treats stacked `#[immune]` attributes as independent coverage entries.
